      <title>写字楼房地产市场崩盘开始在地区性银行浮现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-14/office-property-meltdown-is-starting-to-surface-at-regional-banks-credit-weekly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[办公楼价值的暴跌对美国银行产生了连锁影响，尤其是小型银行，它们在商业房地产账簿上加大了贷款修改的使用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-14/office-property-meltdown-is-starting-to-surface-at-regional-banks-credit-weekly</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 14 Dec 2024 18:47:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
